    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/900e9f7933f4faa34b4a23a07ff8554d.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在不久后的将来，恶魔毫无征兆地出现在了世界各地，并开始大肆破坏人类的生存环境。就在人类即将陷入绝望的境地时，一个神秘的忍者组织突然站了出来。他们拥有常人所不能及的力量与智慧，并发誓要尽全力抹除恶魔的存在，将人类从毁灭的命运中拯救出来，夺回属于人类的和平生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/3d328b9a669c1b5a7392ed66d916c5a7.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=72 /></span>虽然这部作品的战斗系统以传统回合制战斗为主，但您也可以运用周密的计划与细致的操作技巧来避免爆肝！如果您选择以暗杀模式进行战斗的话，就可以在避开绝大多数战斗（BOSS战是无法回避的）的状况下获得正常的奖励哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/026219a93e1229fd057ed7276fd65840.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/31964497c90df3e028ab91d273dedc74.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/ede22630037f25c32356f649813f215c.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219820/extras/3b75da42f4083c758363067558485e9a.avif?t=1749282741\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p>",
